        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has slightly thickened, return the <strong>golden meat-free chick'n</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until the meat-free chick'n has warmed through – this is your <strong>General Tso's meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
