    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> General Tso's meat-free chick'n</strong> over the<strong> cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong> with the <strong>broccoli</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
